Script: a number for the particular combination of counterbalanced variables that an infant got
whether the person reached to the left or the right in hab
Test.PL.Object: whether the teddy bear or the ball was located at the preferred location at test
PL.Starting.Object: whether the object that was at the preferred location in the first hab trial was the teddy bear or the ball
PL.Test.Order: the order in which the person reached to the preferred location in test trials
Video.Quality: a rating of the video's motion quality over Zoom
Device: the device infants watched videos on
Type: the type of test trial (Different Object or Different Location, relative to habituation)
TrialPair: whether the test trial was in the 1st, 2nd, or 3rd pair of test trials
